  {
    "hotel_id": "6723",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/hotel-marais-bastille/hotel/paris-fr.html",
    "name": "Hotel Marais Bastille",
    "detail": "My stay at Hotel Marais Bastille was nearly perfect. This hotel has a modern and somewhat minimal aesthetic that I enjoy. The location is excellent, situated on the edge of Le Marais and near at least four different subway lines that will take you anywhere in the city. The staff were always friendly and provided great service. I also appreciated the email from the hotel about a week before my stay, which asked me to fill out a short questionnaire of my preferences and requests. I requested and was given a double room just like the photos, with a small terrace overlooking the boulevard. I arrived early, thanks to a morning flight, but I was allowed to check in around 2:15pm when my room was ready. The room was larger than most Paris hotel rooms at this price, and it was cleaned very well every day of my stay. The bed was too firm for my taste, but I know everyone has different preferences on that. I appreciated the mini-fridge that was empty so I could fill it with my own food and drink",
