  {
    "hotel_id": "67323",
    "hotel_url": "https://www.agoda.com/la-villa-royale-hotel/hotel/paris-fr.html",
    "name": "La Villa Royale Hotel",
    "detail": "Our aim for a hotel in Paris for my partner’s birthday was to be one that is memorable, unusual, beautifully adorned, rococo (Frenchy?) and not too expensive. the inclusion of balcony with a marvellous view of Sacré-Cœur, a Jacuzzi bath and close proximity of Moulin Rouge made the whole experience one of our very favourites! The area is one to 'experience Paris by night', only a short, rewarding stroll up to Montmartre. This was one of our favourite places of Paris, Place du Tertre, a small square of restaurants with a gathering of artists and fun life-loving musicians. Eating/drinking here you won't be disappointed. Great to then walk back down the hill to the hotel at the end of the night. All the staff were very helpful and polite, Pierluigi (hope I have spelt the name right!) was so lovely and could not do enough to accommodate. Suggesting fantastic restaurants right down to helping us with our flight check-in tickets! This is the place to go, we will love to return here soon!",
    "area": "Opera,Paris - View on map",
